    "export_manifest": "Proof bundle for run-feature-implementation-0001: flow version, 10 events, 2 passed gates with evidence, 4 artifact refs, verdict accepted."
  },
  "notes": "Exports a compact proof bundle for a completed run with the verifier outcome attached."
